          <div class="extensions">
            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer e-admin">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus volume pricing</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                  <span class="category">Admin</span>
                </div>
                <p>Set pricing discounts based on a range of quantities to provide competitive rates for customers buying in bulk.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio-contrib/solidus_volume_pricing" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus multi domain</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Create multiple storefronts and select which products and pricing are displayed on each.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio/solidus_multi_domain" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-backend e-admin">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Avatax certified</h4>
