          <div class="extensions">
            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Amazon payments</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Integrate Amazon Pay into your store’s checkout for a familiar, trusted way for customers to check out.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/boomerdigital/solidus_amazon_payments" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Adyen</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Support credit cards, PayPal, and direct debit payments through the Adyen payment gateway.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/StemboltHQ/solidus-adyen" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Affirm</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
