                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio-contrib/solidus_affirm" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Braintree</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Support credit cards, PayPal, and Apple Pay payments through the Braintree payment gateway.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio/solidus_braintree" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Paybright</h4>
                <div class="categories">
