                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/StemboltHQ/solidus_paybright" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Klarna payments</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Offer flexible financing and monthly payment options to customer using the Klarna service.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/bitspire/solidus_klarna_payments" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus gateway</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Support multiple payment service providers with this easy-to-configure gateway (based on Shopify’s Active Merchant gem).</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio/solidus_gateway" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus virtual gift card</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                </div>
                <p>Add virtual gift card products with unique codes that can apply store credit to a user’s account.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio/solidus_virtual_gift_card" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="extensions-group accordion-item">
        <h4 class="title"><a class="collapsed" href="#" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse6">Shipping <%= inline_svg("icons/arrow-down.svg", class: "isvg isvg-arrow") %></a></h4>

        <div id="collapse6" class="content collapse" data-parent="#accordion">
          <div class="extensions">
            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer e-admin">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus active shipping</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                  <span class="category">Admin</span>
                </div>
                <p>Find shipping rates and provides the ability to register and track shipments with this simple library. Negotiate rates directly with your carrier of choice and use this extension to connect your account. Choose from eight carriers including UPS, USPS, FedEx, Canada Post and more. </p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio-contrib/solidus_active_shipping" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer e-admin">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus Shipstation</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                  <span class="category">Admin</span>
                </div>
                <p>Import, manage, and ship orders using the Shipstation service.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/boomerdigital/solidus_shipstation" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="extension-info card card-border-none e-customer e-admin">
              <div class="card-body">
                <h4 class="title">Solidus EasyPost</h4>
                <div class="categories">
                  <span class="category">Customer-Facing</span>
                  <span class="category">Admin</span>
                </div>
                <p>Compare rates, buy postage, track packages, verify addresses, and more, using the EasyPost service. This service integrates with USPS, UPS, Fedex, DHL, and other popular carriers.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio-contrib/solidus_easypost" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="extensions-group accordion-item">
