                  <span class="category">Backend Functionality</span>
                </div>
                <p>Index product pages and others to generate a sitemap that you can submit to search engines.</p>
                <a class="link" href="https://github.com/solidusio-contrib/solidus_sitemap" target="_blank">Get it on GitHub</a>
              </div>
